flowchart TD
    START["What do you want to show?"] --> C[Compare values]
    START --> D[Show distribution]
    START --> R[Show relationship]
    START --> K[Show composition]
    START --> T[Show change over time]

    C --> C1{How many categories?}
    C1 -->|≤ 7| BAR[Bar / Column chart]
    C1 -->|Many| DOT[Dot plot / Lollipop]
    C --> C2{Ranking matter?} -->|Yes| RANK[Horizontal bar, sorted]

    D --> D1{One variable?} -->|Yes| HIST[Histogram or Box plot]
    D1 -->|Multiple groups| VIO[Violin or Ridge plot]

    R --> R1{How many variables?}
    R1 -->|2| SCAT[Scatter plot]
    R1 -->|Many| PAIR[Pair plot or Heat map]

    K --> PIE{Few categories?} -->|Yes| WPIE["`Pie / Donut (use sparingly)`"]
    PIE -->|No| STACKED[Stacked bar or Treemap]

    T --> LINE[Line chart]
    T --> AREA["`Area chart (for cumulative)`"]
